{"tid":783153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油麻地彌敦道鬧市發生跳樓 38歲男子身亡","createTime":"2018-08-17T10:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T10:39:21.000Z","uid":42188,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0f50e2065e9b827e9b29723285da8a68094ffce5","tid":783153,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"下午3時許，一輛行走117線隧道巴士在油麻地沿彌敦道北行，途至515號至517號近窩打老道口停車候燈期間，一名男子墮樓，擊中巴士左尾車身再著地重傷，車長發覺慌忙報警，期間有路人誤以為巴士撞倒路人，亦致電報警，警方接報到場證實有人墮樓擊中巴士，惟在巴士與行人路之間倒臥血泊男子證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n男死者38歲，警方懷疑他由好收成商業大廈墮下，經上樓調查，證實死者是15樓一間教育機構的職員，正調查其墮樓原因。"},{"pid":"1657ee82cbb3de06706b102da115e2de2689720d","tid":783153,"uid":42513,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:23:56.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拿拿聲收屍唔洗阻住收工"},{"pid":"b55e4e259915390d0d0ea7b84ba885817d98e283","tid":783153,"uid":10692,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:24:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"225b443c175da56a8b9e8c8262b0c12081505411","tid":783153,"uid":619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:24:57.000Z","msg":"咩叫發生跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7047c8be767662dcf81f0ea7fd7cc9427f74c4bd","tid":783153,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:25:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d4317a988f303b09d66bd17baa4c51db72a5ad9","tid":783153,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 3時許"},{"pid":"920899cfb3a11cca47b90b1a745be5421fd4825e","tid":783153,"uid":116289,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"225b443c175da56a8b9e8c8262b0c12081505411","tid":783153,"uid":619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c